## Rails Testing Stack

Rails 8 uses **Minitest** by default (simple, fast, built-in).

### Test Types

1. **Model Tests** - Test models, validations, associations, methods
2. **Controller Tests** - Test controller actions, responses
3. **System Tests** - Test full user interactions (browser automation)
4. **Job Tests** - Test background jobs
5. **Mailer Tests** - Test email delivery
6. **Helper Tests** - Test view helpers

